{"tid":150363,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AV女優搶走男朋友 井上真央崩潰傳密謀退出演藝圈","createTime":"2017-03-10T03:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T10:44:13.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61ae251c47b048f751044dc9a4b0c990536abfe7","tid":150363,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:52:16.000Z","msg":"日本女星井上真央從童星起家，2005年主演日版《流星花園》的「杉菜」爆紅，外傳和「嵐」松本潤交往多年，一度論及婚嫁，怎料男方卻被踢爆偷吃AV女優葵司（葵つかさ），讓她心碎一地，現在更被指出她因為打擊太大，推掉許多工作邀約，有可能因此告別演藝圈。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1745/d1745829.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1745%2Fd1745829.jpg&h=d48d25cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲井上真央爆出和松本潤婚事告吹。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《日刊cyzo》報導，井上真央和松本潤地下情發展多年，卻被踢爆男方劈腿AV女優葵司長達4年，自己則是像傻子一般渾然不知，因此打消原本打算結婚的想法，據悉，她推掉3000萬日幣（約840萬台幣）的代言工作，引發揣測可能是情傷未癒，才無心於工作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5754/22517607267_07027d7752_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5754%2F22517607267_07027d7752_c.jpg&h=969d85e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲葵司被爆介入井上真央戀情。<br />\n<br />\n井上真央向來工作態度認真，這次反常推掉工作，引發各界議論，業界盛傳她因為無法接受被劈腿的打擊，有可能宣布退出演藝圈，許多粉絲相當震驚錯愕，但經紀公司尚未出面回應。"},{"pid":"510e227e43abc59640e9873b49735be966057539","tid":150363,"uid":58,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"真司<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693875cbcc351de10cc47a1ff0d7a410d514806a","tid":150363,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:12:18.000Z","msg":"尿潤正仆街"},{"pid":"8ed42177327f647b766d8137957c5ac261980b2e","tid":150363,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"Seed 呢"},{"pid":"7d2219b38cd3e872f2c1639288b4f8210eb0335e","tid":150363,"uid":10244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:15:13.000Z","msg":"張圖做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f208546dcde9499399f25042e3beefc4f5b3bca3","tid":150363,"uid":33443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:22:52.000Z","msg":"真央<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5dc38d290f6ede9d772a6dc8f60edc8c108a39","tid":150363,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"密謀加入av界就話啫"},{"pid":"2d65d8478322e88873e71b12ab2eb80136d1e693","tid":150363,"uid":3983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"朱千雪呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}